## List service bindings

```
Definition
```

```http
GET /v3/service_bindings HTTP/1.1
```

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.[your-domain.com]/v3/service_bindings" \
  -X GET \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]"
```

```
Example Response
```

```http
HTTP/1.1 200 OK

<%= yield_content :paginated_list_of_service_bindings, '/v3/service_bindings' %>
```

